Introduction

JiYeon is a South Korean singer and dancer under MODHAUS.

On April 4, 2024, JiYeon was introduced as the twenty-fourth and last member of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS. She debuted with tripleS on May 8, 2024, with the album "ASSEMBLE24".

As a member of tripleS, JiYeon was placed in the sub-units Glow and Visionary Vision.
